    "critical_context": "Marine plasma is sourced from the ocean. Unlike synthetic electrolytes, ocean-sourced minerals carry inherent risks: heavy metal contamination (mercury, lead, arsenic, cadmium), microbiological contamination, and environmental pollutants. Third-party testing is not optional - it is a regulatory and brand trust requirement. Every batch must be tested. COA (Certificate of Analysis) publication builds trust and differentiates from competitors who make purity claims without evidence.",
